Install:

1) cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
2) make
3) make install

You might need to run kbuildsycoca4 and restart plasma in order to be able to 
add this plasmoid

Uninstall:

1) make uninstall

Test it:

Usefull to get some traceback when you encounter problems :)

1) plasmoidviewer plasma_applet_emergelog
